    &lt;strong
      &gt;Nguồn tham khảo: &lt;a href=&quot;/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Viettel CSKH&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong
    &gt;
  &lt;/p&gt;
