  &lt;/p&gt;
 
&lt;/div&gt;
</content><link rel='replies' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.sinvoice.vn/feeds/7989337464344048828/comments/default' title='Đăng Nhận xét'/><link rel='replies' type='text/html' href='https://www.sinvoice.vn/2023/03/thoi-diem-cap-va-thu-tuc-nop-chung-tu-khau-tru-thue-tncn-2023.html#comment-form' title='0 Nhận xét'/><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/8243747611808165490/posts/default/7989337464344048828'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/8243747611808165490/posts/default/7989337464344048828'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://www.sinvoice.vn/2023/03/thoi-diem-cap-va-thu-tuc-nop-chung-tu-khau-tru-thue-tncn-2023.html' title='Thời điểm cấp và thủ tục nộp chứng từ khấu trừ thuế TNCN 2023'/><author><name>Văn Tài</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/02264579707873986017</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='32' height='32' src='//blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgUH-cYVfJi5WNJJQvElvzE0I2M_7ys2wlhupd2WgcgXSX2-Ug7kPM1wp7ge4zK6k53helIZjXuoBwvJzpAxxwh53xLWbryapXEFnFuT36zJR-esd6HZEZ_fAG165TRseE/s220/SINVOICE-01.png'/></author><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEibstRDRYwKA_Ml7MTJoQWSiQUJO3xu8TkcL3R3YHAWG6ydU5om7G2g0g51CRAJr7fyU9-ltdlJhhGkqylv9HQRGWuE3ZQ-Ti_d3-4rrrVU1enON3p8ipwK2ATzL9uTOuajmHi566VX7xWlNYtJZIwL8lG78tmoa-NCkZuXqL_UnoDuEAN-PrlWHXeMKA/s72-c/thoi-diem-cap-va-thu-tuc-nop-chung-tu-khau-tru-thue-tncn-2023.webp" height="72" width="72"/><thr:total>0</thr:total></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8243747611808165490.post-3434100470308070313</id><published>2023-03-10T21:16:00.006+07:00</published><updated>2025-05-03T11:07:24.908+07:00</updated><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="Bản tin"/><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="Hóa đơn điện tử S-Invoice"/><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="tin-tuc"/><title type='text'>Sử dụng chứng từ khấu trừ Thuế TNCN theo quy định tại Nghị định 123/2020/NĐ-CP</title><content type='html'>&lt;script type=&quot;application/ld+json&quot;&gt;
