</content><link rel='replies' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.sinvoice.vn/feeds/8646136458578501693/comments/default' title='Đăng Nhận xét'/><link rel='replies' type='text/html' href='https://www.sinvoice.vn/2023/03/chung-tu-thue-dien-tu-khong-bat-buoc-chuyen-du-lieu-sang-co-quan-thue.html#comment-form' title='0 Nhận xét'/><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/8243747611808165490/posts/default/8646136458578501693'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='https://www.blogger.com/feeds/8243747611808165490/posts/default/8646136458578501693'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='https://www.sinvoice.vn/2023/03/chung-tu-thue-dien-tu-khong-bat-buoc-chuyen-du-lieu-sang-co-quan-thue.html' title='Chứng từ điện tử không bắt buộc đăng ký, thông báo phát hành, chuyển dữ liệu đến Cơ quan Thuế'/><author><name>Văn Tài</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/02264579707873986017</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='32' height='32' src='//blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgUH-cYVfJi5WNJJQvElvzE0I2M_7ys2wlhupd2WgcgXSX2-Ug7kPM1wp7ge4zK6k53helIZjXuoBwvJzpAxxwh53xLWbryapXEFnFuT36zJR-esd6HZEZ_fAG165TRseE/s220/SINVOICE-01.png'/></author><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiQ06XaD5uq4MZbbqAv6RxHomCu51iEbfcMJgIG91hCoKMM4BI2e5ZwSrEJqnZcHQuS-o_5OaFxe4igIA3sxMx0epkv9X2iY9RUulpD8cSLfT36PH0zy9oTtU-3gKbKvomJMuG5JEwkLkHKYvefxdZGlOjiFA1BUf6_SnxZj-guJncigCbruHFfnDPfnw/s72-c/chung-tu-dien-tu-khong-can-gui-den-cqt.webp" height="72" width="72"/><thr:total>0</thr:total></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8243747611808165490.post-1986287288515718921</id><published>2023-03-01T22:47:00.012+07:00</published><updated>2025-05-03T11:09:52.869+07:00</updated><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="Bản tin"/><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="Hóa đơn điện tử S-Invoice"/><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="tin-tuc"/><title type='text'>Tem/vé/thẻ điện tử Viettel – Quy định về tem/vé/thẻ điện tử theo Thông tư 78/2021/TT-BTC</title><content type='html'>&lt;script type=&quot;application/ld+json&quot;&gt;
